          	  <span class="gn13b">[1968-6 台灣教會公報 文類-散文 作者--/-]</span>
          	            	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-11513.htm">台南神學院開校友大會 [ Tâi-lâm Sîn-ha̍k-īⁿ khui hāu-iú tāi-hoē ]</a></span>
          	  <br />
              <span class="gy12">...<a href="artical-11513.htm"><img src="../images/btn_more.gif" hspace="5" border="0" align="absmiddle" /></a></span>
